## 重跑机制

重跑在主进程串行执行（不用子进程），因为只需跑一个段：
```python
_init_indicator_cache(coin, interval, new_slice, db_path=':memory:')
eng = BacktestEngine(coin=coin, interval=interval, days=0, candles=new_slice)
signals = eng.generate_signals(strategy_name)
for m in modes:
    sim = TradeSimulator(new_slice, signals, mode=m, ...)
    new_trades[m] = [(t序列化) for t in sim.run()]
```

